== Selected Publications

* indicates equal contributions

1. *Shuyang Li*, Qiang Wu, Ran Wang. Dynamic Discrete Topology Design and Routing for Satellite-Terrestrial Integrated Networks. IEEE/ACM Transactions on Networking, 2024. {{<span class="text-red">(CCF-A)</span>}}

2. *Shuyang Li*, Qiang Wu, Ran Wang, et al. Efficient Multipath Differential Routing and Traffic Scheduling in Ultra-Dense LEO Satellite Networks: A DRL with Stackelberg Game Approach. IEEE Transactions on Mobile Computing, 2025. {{<span class="text-red">(CCF-A, 中科院一区, IF=9.2)</span>}}

3. *Shuyang Li*, Qiang Wu, Ran Wang, et al. Efficient Packet Routing for Large-Scale LEO Satellite Networks: A Pareto-Optimal MARL Approach with Queueing Theory. IEEE Internet of Things Journal, 2025. {{<span class="text-red">(中科院一区, IF=8.9)</span>}}

4. *Shuyang Li*, Qiang Wu, Ran Wang, et al. Towards Networking and Routing in 6G Satellite-Terrestrial Integrated Networks: Current Issues and a Potential Solution. IEEE Communications Magazine, 2025. {{<span class="text-red">(中科院二区, IF=8.2)</span>}}

5. *Shuyang Li*, Qiang Wu, Ran Wang. Efficient Packet Routing in Ultra-Dense LEO Satellite Networks via Cooperative-MARL with Queuing Theory Model. In: 2025 IEEE Wireless Communications and Networking Conference (WCNC). IEEE, 2025: 1-6. {{<span class="text-red">(通信类旗舰会议)</span>}}

6. *Shuyang Li*, Xiaohui Hu, Yongwen Du. Deep reinforcement learning and game theory for computation offloading in dynamic edge computing markets. IEEE Access, 2021, 9: 121456-121466. {{<span class="text-red">(Citations: 50)</span>}}

7. *Shuyang Li*, Xiaohui Hu, Yongwen Du. Deep reinforcement learning for computation offloading and resource allocation in unmanned-aerial-vehicle assisted edge computing. Sensors, 2021, 21(19): 6499. {{<span class="text-red">(Citations: 43)</span>}}

8. Wanyue Li\*, *Shuyang Li\* *, Jie Hao, et al. Efficient Task Offloading and Resource Allocation in HAPS-Assisted LEO Satellite Networks: A MAPPO with Exact Potential Game Approach. IEEE Internet of Things Journal, 2025. {{<span class="text-red">(中科院一区，IF=8.9)</span>}}

9. Xiquan Zhang, Jianwu Dang, Yangping Wang, and *Shuyang Li*. MCCI: A multi-channel collaborative interaction framework for multimodal knowledge graph completion. Information Processing & Management, 2025, 62(4): 104156. {{<span class="text-red">(CCF-B, 中科院一区, IF=6.9)</span>}}

10. Xiquan Zhang, Jianwu Dang, Yangping Wang, and *Shuyang Li*. Feature enhancement based on hierarchical reconstruction framework for inductive prediction on sparse graphs. Information Processing & Management, 2025, 62(1): 103894. {{<span class="text-red">(CCF-B, 中科院一区, IF=6.9)</span>}}

