12. Wanyue Li, *Shuyang Li*, Jie Hao, et al. Efficient Task Offloading and Resource Allocation in Space-Air-Ground-Sea Networks: A MAPPO-based Approach. International Conference on Wireless Artificial Intelligent Computing Systems and Applications (WASA). Springer, 2025. {{<span class="text-red">(CCF-C)</span>}}

